    <item>
      <title>耶伦：石油市场疲软或意味着对俄罗斯采取更多行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/yellen-softer-oil-market-may-mean-more-action-on-russia-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，美国不断加强对俄罗斯的制裁，并一直在寻找创造性的方法来限制俄罗斯的收入。她在“彭博公开利息”节目中与大卫·古拉进行了交谈。（更正记者姓名。）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/yellen-softer-oil-market-may-mean-more-action-on-russia-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 16:01:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
